*                                           (put your own printf's here)
*   #define TEST_ABORT                    - code to test for ^C or abort
*                                           (called on each pixel)
*   #define FINISH_POVRAY              - last statement before exiting normally
*   #define COOPERATE                    - called for multi-tasking
*  
